commit.title: [ci] [docker] Pin specific versions of OPAM CI dependencies.
commit.message:
[ci] [docker] Pin specific versions of OPAM CI dependencies.

Things like Menhir or Elpi seem to fragile as to allow a
non-deterministic install in the Dockefile, we thus specify the
version for all `CI_OPAM` packages.

cc: https://github.com/AbsInt/CompCert/issues/234
